No. 80,

Misc.

Ladner v. United States. Petitioner pro se. Solicitor General Rankin, Assistant Attorney General Olney and Beatrice Rosenberg for the United States.

Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit granted.

Mr. Justice Brennan took no part in the consideration or decision of these applications.
